Name: Thieve's Auction
Rules Text: Set aside all cards in play. Starting with you, each player chooses one of the cards set aside and puts it into play tapped under his or her control. Repeat this process until all those cards have been chosen.

Name: Thieving Magpie
Rules Text:
Flying.
Whenever Thieving Magpie deals damage to an opponent, you draw a card.
Flavor Text: Other birds collect twigs for their nests. Magpies steal jewels for theirs.

Name: Thron Elemental
Rules Text: You may have Thorn Elemental deal its combat damage to defending player as though it weren’t blocked.
Flavor Text: Rain from this storm leaves you pinned to the ground like an insect.

Name: Tidal Kraken
Rules Text: Tidal Kraken is unblockable.
Flavor Text: To merfolk, pirates are a nuisance. To pirates, merfolk are a threat. To the kraken, they’re both appetizers.

Name: Trade Routes
Rules Text:
|1: Return target land you control to its owner’s hand.
|1, Discard a land card from your hand: Draw a card.
Flavor Text: The wise, the righteous, the mighty—the merchant feeds them all.

Name: Treasure Trove
Rules Text: |2|U|U: Draw a card.
Flavor Text:
“Wealth means power; the power to subdue, to crush, to exploit, the power to enslave, to outrage, to degrade.” 
—Emma Goldman, “Anarchism”

Name: Tremor
Rules Text: Tremor deals 1 damage to each creature without flying.
Flavor Text: Where do you run when the earth becomes your enemy?

Name: Two-Headed Dragon
Rules Text:
Flying
|1|R: Two-Headed Dragon gets +2/+0 until end of turn. 
Two-Headed Dragon can’t be blocked except by two or more creatures. 
Two-Headed Dragon may block an additional creature.

Name: Urza's Armor
Rules Text: If a source would deal damage to you, prevent 1 of that damage.
Flavor Text: Urza protected his body well, but neglected his soul.

Name: Vampiric Spirit
Rules Text:
Flying
When Vampiric Spirit comes into play, you lose 4 life.

Name: Venerable Monk
Rules Text: When Venerable Monk comes into play, you gain 2 life.
Flavor Text: Age wears the flesh but galvanizes the soul.

Name: Vernal Bloom
Rules Text: Whenever |Ha Forest is tapped for mana, its controller adds  |G to his or her mana pool.
Flavor Text: The sun breaks, the beasts stir, and the forest awakens to stand against its enemies.

Name: Vexing Arcanix
Rules Text:
|3,|T : Target player names a card, then reveals the top card of his or her library. If it's the named card, the player puts it into his or her hand.
Otherwise, the player puts it into his or her graveyard and Vexing Arcanix deals 2 damage to him or her.

Name: Viashino Sandstalker
Rules Text:
Haste
At end of turn, return Viashino Sandstalker to its owner's hand.
Flavor Text: "Some believe sandstalkers to be illusions; those with scars know better." —Zhalfirin Guide to the Desert

Name: Vicious Hunger
Rules Text: Vicious Hunger deals 2 damage to target creature and you gain 2 life.
Flavor Text: Only the most ravenous soul feeds on the health of the weak.

Name: Vine Trellis
Rules Text:
(Walls can't attack.)
|T: Add |G to your mana pool.
Flavor Text: Nature twists knots stronger than any rope.

Name: Volcanic Hammer
Rules Text: Volcanic Hammer deals 3 damage to target creature or player.
Flavor Text: Fire finds its form in the heat of the forge.

Name: Warped Devotion
Rules Text: Whenever a permanent is returned to a player's hand, that player discards a card from his or her hand.
Flavor Text:
"The spirit of the devout is easily crushed by the loss of hope."
—Fallen angel

Name: WesterPaladin
Rules Text: |B|B,|T : Destroy target |Swhite creature.
Flavor Text:
"Expect nothing but scorn, flattery, and lies. And never turn your back on him."
—Northern paladin

Name: Wing Snare
Rules Text: Destroy target creature with flying.
Flavor Text:
"We are the hands of the great trees, reaching out to ensnare what threatens their branches."
—Elvish hunter

Name: Wood Elves
Rules Text: When Wood Elves comes into play, search your library for |Ha Forest card and put that card into play. Then shuffle your library.
Flavor Text: Every branch a crossroads, every vine a swift steed.

Name: Worship
Rules Text: If you control a creature, damage that would reduce your life total to less than 1 reduces it to 1 instead.
Flavor Text:
"Believe in the ideal, not the idol."
—Serra

Name: Wrath of Marit Lage
Rules Text:
When Wrath of Marit Lage comes into play, tap all |Sred creatures.
|SRed creatures don't untap during their controllers' untap steps.
Flavor Text:
"Marit Lage lies frozen in a glacier's heart. Still her dreams take form in our world, stealing the heat from our souls."
—Halvor Arenson, Kjeldoran priest

Name: Yavimaya Enchantress
Rules Text: Yavimaya Enchantress gets +1/+1 for each enchantment in play.
Flavor Text: Her roots connect her to the forest's wishes.

Name: Suntail Hawk
Rules Text: Flying
Flavor Text: Its eye the glaring sun, its cry the keening wind.

Name: Trained Armodon
Flavor Text: Armodons are trained to step on things. Enemy things.

Name: Wind drake
Rules Text: Flying
Flavor Text:
"But high she shoots through air and light,
Above all low delay,
Where nothing earthly bounds her flight,
Nor shadow dims her way."
—Thomas Moore, "Oh that I had Wings"

Name: Akroma, Angel of Wrath
Rules Text:
Flying, first strike, trample, haste, protection from |Sblack, protection from |Sred
Attacking doesn't cause Akroma, Angel of Wrath to tap.
